OL,3,CControversial farming scheme delayed
OL,4,Cby a year say Welsh Government
OL,6,FThe introduction of the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment's sustainable farming
OL,8,Fscheme has been delayed by a year,
OL,9,Fit's been announced.
OL,11,FThe new rural affairs secretary, Huw
OL,12,FIrranca-Davies, confirmed the news at
OL,13,Fa visit to a farm in Bridgend today,
OL,14,F14 May.
OL,16,FSpeaking at a press conference at
OL,17,FSealands Farm in Bridgend, the Cabinet
OL,18,FSecretary said that the change of
OL,19,Ftimings was part of his "commitment to
OL,20,Fmeaningful engagement with the farming
OL,21,Fsector."
