OL,6,FHe said: "Since the first day of
OL,7,Ftaking up this role I have been out
OL,8,Fand about meeting and listening to our
OL,9,Ffarmers, hearing their views and
OL,10,Ftaking on board what they have to say.
OL,12,F"My commitment to meaningful
OL,13,Fengagement with the farming sector,
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru colleagues under the
OL,15,FCooperation Agreement and other
OL,16,Fstakeholders on the changes needed
OL,17,Fwill necessitate a change in the
OL,18,Fimplementation timetable.
