OL,6,F"We have always said the Scheme would
OL,7,Fnot be introduced until it is ready
OL,8,Fand I stand by that."
OL,10,FHe then confirmed that the Basic
OL,11,FPayment Scheme would continue to be
OL,12,Favailable in 2025, with the proposed
OL,13,FSFS (Sustainable Farming Scheme)
OL,14,Ftransition period starting from 2026,
OL,15,Fwith an announcement to follow on the
OL,16,FBPS ceiling.
OL,18,FExisting rural investment schemes,
OL,19,Fsuch as the small grants schemes, will
OL,20,Fcontinue to support infrastructure
OL,21,Fchanges, say the Welsh government.
