OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives said the
OL,7,Fstatement from Mr Irranca-Davies was
OL,8,F"encouraging."
OL,10,F"It's a positive step to see that the
OL,11,FMinister has listened to the industry,
OL,12,Fthe unions, and all those thousands of
OL,13,Fpeople who responded to the
OL,14,Fconsultation", said James Evans MS,
OL,15,FShadow Rural Affairs Minister.
OL,17,F"However, what we need to see is real
OL,18,Fchange to SFS in its current form.
